content: Great app, but in trying to download to my tablet it is requesting that I pay for it again! They are both on the same Google account.

Works well on my phone, however it has a lot of issues on my chromebook which is what we typically use to practice between weekly speech sessions. The app is laid out well for my 6 year old. However he does need help with it. This isn't and independant app for children to use. They will need help to use the app as I believe intended.
Did not work. Could not make selections and did not have sound.
replyContent:
We are sorry to know that you are having some problems with the app. It seems that you are having some problems with setting up required permissions for the app. Can you please email us at support@articulationessentials.com
Our technical team will assist you to make sure that you get the app working properly on your device.

Thanks.
